      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for a buyer who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining from years of use. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that simply needs some TLC to be brought back to its best.",
