    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's analog peak, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is routed through a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is well-sorted, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already completed to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve adjustment and a VANOS solenoid refresh. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain remains robust, delivering linear power delivery and the signature metallic rasp of a healthy S54 engine. It sits on factory Style 67 wheels wrapped in high-performance rubber, ready for immediate spirited use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
